entry.summary:
  We give two proofs of the identity $$\sqrt{\frac{\cos\frac{2\pi}{5}}
{\cos\frac{\pi}{5}}}+\sqrt{\frac{\cos\frac{\pi}{5}} {\cos\frac{2\pi}{5}}
}=\sqrt{5},$$ using and not using the gold ratio.

